# ── Remote session ID lookup (CLAUDE_CODE_REMOTE_SESSION_ID) ─────────────────
# Set at runtime by the SessionStart hook once the env var is available.
# Key pattern: session:remote:<cse_id>:context → agent_sessions context blob
# Key pattern: session:remote:<cse_id>:branch  → git branch for this session
# Transcript URL: https://claude.ai/code/${CLAUDE_CODE_REMOTE_SESSION_ID/#cse_/session_}
# Source: vendor/anthropics/code.claude.com/docs/en/claude-code-on-the-web.md
#
# To populate when running in a web session:
#   redis-cli SET "session:remote:${CLAUDE_CODE_REMOTE_SESSION_ID}:context" \
#     "$(redis-cli GET session:2026-06-17:context)" EX 604800
#   redis-cli SET "session:remote:${CLAUDE_CODE_REMOTE_SESSION_ID}:branch" \
#     "$(redis-cli GET session:2026-06-17:branch)" EX 604800

